        "kicker_1": "Proprietary Technology",
        "heading_1": "WOC AI Wellness Engine™",
        "description_1": "Our proprietary AI processor analyses your body in real-time — from muscle tension and blood circulation to stress levels and sleep quality. With over 200 sensor data points, BioVis Pro® adapts every single massage session to your body’s exact needs.",
        "bullets": "<p>Real-time body analysis with 200+ sensor data points</p><p>Adaptive massage intensity based on muscle tension</p><p>AI-driven health monitoring (pulse, blood pressure, stress)</p><p>Self-learning algorithm — improves with every session</p>",
        "kicker_2": "AI-Driven Health",
        "heading_2": "AI Health Detection",
        "description_2": "The World of Comfort BioVis Pro® features an advanced health monitoring system that measures key indicators such as fatigue level, heart rate, oxygen saturation, microcirculation, and heart rate variability."
